name: South_Shore_Chocolate_Axess_5-shelf_Bookcase
reviews: I purchased 2 of these and they were easy to assemble. It says it takes 2 people, but I did it myself. They are sturdy, and look nice too. The only downside is the screw covers don't fit well, and if you try to force them in, they break.

This is a very good bookshelf. We are happy with the color and of the size of the shelves. Unfortunately, on each of the side there are chips in the wood. Even placing it against the wall is upsetting cause you can see a chip in the wood still from both sides. It is very noticeable.
Love it but don't get how the top piece fits on there so it isn't on there for now :/
This bookcase is very nice. Came in one carton. Very heavy. Color was spot on to picture on web site. Good quality for the money.
Very nice but too narrow for a bookcase
